\title{Previewing PRs}
\author{samueltoth}
\date{2026-06-07}
\import{stt-macros}

\p{Once you open a pull request (with a commit that passes the CI
checks), you will be able to access a rendered preview of the changes
at \code{http://agda-synthetic-categories/preview/<PR_NUMBER>}.}

\subtree{
\taxon{Warning}
\p{This feature is still in an experimental state}
}
